    Teka Singapore - 
    Your Trusted Kitchen Electrical Appliances Brand

    Teka is a global brand that provides innovative and high-quality kitchen appliances to consumers all over the world. With a focus on design, functionality, and durability, Teka products are designed to make daily tasks easier and more enjoyable. From cooker hoods and induction cooker hobs to built in ovens and microwave ovens, our products are built to meet the highest standards of quality and reliability.

     

    Our company is founded in Germany with a century-long reputation for quality, technology, and innovation, and is dedicated to achieving excellence in every aspect.

     

    At Teka Singapore, we share this passion and firmly believe that healthy and nutritious meals are essential to a happy and fulfilling life. Yet, we understand that busy working Singaporeans often struggle to cook meals at home, especially with the abundance of cheap yet unhealthy hawker food. That’s why we’re on a mission to revolutionise healthy home cooking, no matter how busy one’s schedule is. By merging the power of technology and innovation, we’re simplifying the cooking process while maintaining exceptional standards for quality.

     

    We’re thrilled to embark on this journey and committed to positively impacting the lives of people in Singapore and beyond, one delectable and healthy meal at a time.
